    "This coincided with an increase in the number of neighboring cells in regenerating portal vessels for all cell types except hepatocytes (Supplementary Fig. 17g).",
    "Furthermore, immune cells in regenerating tissue, unlike in healthy or embolized, had a higher proportion of vessel stroma cells as immediate neighbors (Supplementary Fig. 17h).",
